    <section class="section" id="chromaticity">
        <h2>Chromaticity Diagram</h2>
        <p>
            The chromaticity diagram is a critical tool for analyzing colors and interpreting 
            results. Engineers use this for calibration and measurement systems.
        </p>
        <div class="simulation" id="chromaticity-simulation">
