        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="applications">
        <h2>Applications in Optical Engineering</h2>
        <p>
            Optical Test Engineers utilize CIE 1931 for calibration, spectroradiometers, and 
            ensuring color consistency. It is especially useful in display technology and 
            LEDs.
        </p>
